(32, 11, '_request_body', '{"product":{"title":"Hou00e0ng Mai Huu1ebf","id":8,"created_at":"2015-01-03T00:59:31Z","updated_at":"2015-03-23T08:46:58Z","type":"simple","status":"publish","downloadable":false,"virtual":false,"permalink":"http://localhost/saigonhoa/?product=hoang-mai-hue","sku":"hmh02","price":"1200000.00","regular_price":"1200000.00","sale_price":null,"price_html":"<span class="amount">&#36;1.200.000,00</span>","taxable":false,"tax_status":"taxable","tax_class":"","managing_stock":false,"stock_quantity":0,"in_stock":true,"backorders_allowed":false,"backordered":false,"sold_individually":false,"purchaseable":true,"featured":false,"visible":true,"catalog_visibility":"visible","on_sale":false,"weight":null,"dimensions":{"length":"","width":"","height":"","unit":"cm"},"shipping_required":true,"shipping_taxable":true,"shipping_class":"","shipping_class_id":null,"description":"<p><strong>Huu1ebf khu00f4ng phu1ea3i lu00e0 u0111u1ecba phu01b0u01a1ng duy nhu1ea5t tru1ed3ng mai, chu01a1i mai. Nhu01b0ng khu00f4ng phu1ea3i vu00f4 cu1edb mu00e0 giu1eefa mu1ed9t "tu1eadp u0111ou00e0n" mai Bu00ecnh u0110u1ecbnh, Phu00fa Yu00ean, cu00e1c tu1ec9nh miu1ec1n Tu00e2y Nam bu1ed9 hay thu1eadm chu00ed cu1ea3 mai ru1eebng Bu00ecnh Thuu1eadn tu1ecfa su1eafc khoe hu01b0u01a1ng thu00ec mai vu00e0ng xu1ee9 Huu1ebf - Hou00e0ng Mai, Mai Ngu1ef1 - vu1eabn u0111u01b0u1ee3c du00e2n su00e0nh u0111iu1ec7u nhu1eafc u0111u1ebfn nhiu1ec1u nhu1ea5t.</strong></p>n<p>u0110u00e0nh ru1eb1ng vu1edbi mai kiu1ec3ng, tiu00eau chu00ed cu1ee9 phu1ea3i u201cnhu1ea5t u0111u1ebf, nhu00ec thu00e2n, tam tu1ea7ng, tu1ee9 giu1ed1ngu201d. u0110u1ebf - gu1ed1c -u00a0cu00e0ng lu00e3o thu00ec cu00e0ng giu00e1 tru1ecb, nhu01b0ng thu00e2n mu00e0 tru1ee5i lu1ee7i (khu00f4ng cu00f3 nhu00e1nh) thu00ec cu0169ng vu1ee9t. Ku1ebf u0111u1ebfn lu00e0 tu1ea7ng, cu0169ng nhu01b0 ru1ed3ng, nhu01b0 hu1ed5, phu1ea3i nhiu1ec1u vu00e2y nhiu1ec1u vuu1ed1t mu1edbi tu1ecf u0111u01b0u1ee3c cu00e1i uy, cu00e1i u0111u1eb9p u0111u1eb7c tru01b0ng cu1ee7a mu00ecnh. Ba yu1ebfu tu1ed1 tru00ean hu1ed9i u0111u1ee7 vu1eabn chu01b0a thu1ec3 u0111u00e1nh giu00e1 u0111u01b0u1ee3c mu1ed9t gu1ed1c mai u0111u1ea1t chuu1ea9n nu1ebfu nhu01b0 giu1ed1ng mai u0111u00f3 khu00f4ng phu1ea3i lu00e0 hou00e0ng mai u201cF1u201d, nghu0129a lu00e0 phu1ea3i mai vu00e0ng mu00e0 lu00e0 mai vu00e0ng xu1ee9 Huu1ebf.</p>n<div><span class="TT_TinChiTiet_NoiDung">u00a0</span></div>n<div><span class="TT_TinChiTiet_NoiDung">Mu00e0 cu00e1i giu1ed1ng hou00e0ng mai cu0169ng lu1ea1, u0111u00e3 u0111u1ecfng u0111u1ea3nh, khu00f3 tru1ed3ng lu1ea1i cu00f2n khu00f3 uu1ed1n cu00e0nh do u0111u1ed9 du1ebbo cu1ee7a cu00e0nh ku00e9m hu01a1n hu1ed3ng diu1ec7p mai. Cu0169ng vu00ec lu1ebd u0111u00f3, mu1ed9t khi tu1ea1o ra nhu1eefng thu1ebf mai u0111u01b0u1ee3c xem lu00e0 u201cmu00f4 phu1ea1mu201d nhu01b0 long giu00e1ng, long vu00e2n, tu1ee9 diu1ec7n, hu1ed5 phu1ee5 sinh hu1ed5 tu1eed, long mu1eabu xuu1ea5t long nhi... thu00ec giu00e1 tru1ecb cu1ee7a hou00e0ng mai cu00e0ng cao ngu1ea5t ngu01b0u1ee1ng.</span></div>n<div><span class="TT_TinChiTiet_NoiDung">u00a0</span></div>n<div><span class="TT_TinChiTiet_NoiDung">So vu1edbi mai Bu00ecnh u0110u1ecbnh, Phu00fa Yu00ean, cu00e1c tu1ec9nh miu1ec1n Tu00e2y Nam bu1ed9 hay thu1eadm chu00ed mai ru1eebng Bu00ecnh Thuu1eadn thu00ec mai Huu1ebf lu1ea1 lu1eafm, khu00e1c lu1eafm. Tu1eeb cu00e2y con cho u0111u1ebfn khi ra hoa, ngu01b0u1eddi chu01a1i phu1ea3i chu1edd u0111u1ebfn 7-8 nu0103m (mai cu00e1c tu1ec9nh khu00e1c chu1ec9 u0111u1ed9 4-5 nu0103m). Thu1eddi gian chu0103m bu00f3n lu00e2u hu01a1n hu1eb3n mai u1edf u0111u1ecba phu01b0u01a1ng khu00e1c khiu1ebfn phu1ea7n thu00e2n, phu1ea7n gu1ed1c su1ea7n su00f9i, nu1ee9t nu1ebb xanh ru00eau. Mai Huu1ebf khu00f4ng nhiu1ec1u cu00e1nh, du00e0y bu00f4ng, trung bu00ecnh mu1ed7i hoa chu1ec9 khou1ea3ng 5 cu00e1nh, nhu01b0ng mu00e0u vu00e0ng ru1ef1c ru1ee1 hu01a1n, mu00f9i thu01a1m hu01a1n. Mai Ngu1ef1 lu1ea1i cu00e0ng khu00e1c. Ngou00e0i nhu1eefng u0111u1eb7c u0111iu1ec3m nhu01b0 hou00e0ng mai thu00ec mai Ngu1ef1u00a0lu00e1 du00e0i hu00ecnh ru0103ng cu01b0a, mu1ed7i nu0103m ra hoa 2 lu1ea7n vu00e0o mu00f9a Xuu00e2n vu00e0 mu00f9a Thu.u00a0Hoa cu00f3 su1eafc mu00e0u vu00e0ng u0111u1eadm, hu01b0u01a1ng thu01a1m, nu1ee5 to. Nghe ngu01b0u1eddi giu00e0 ku1ec3 lu1ea1i, giu1ed1ng mai nu00e0y tru01b0u1edbc u0111u00e2y chu1ec9 u0111u01b0u1ee3c tru1ed3ng trong u0110u1ea1i Nu1ed9i.</span></div>n<div>Tu1eeb hu1ea1t u0111u1ebfn khi mai lu1edbn, ra hoa, ngu01b0u1eddi chu01a1i phu1ea3i mu1ea5t 7-8 nu0103m cu00f4ng phu. Nhu01b0ng u0111u00f3 lu00e0 nu00f3i tu1ed5ng thu1ec3, chung chung, chu1ee9 trong 7-8 nu0103m u0111u00f3, cu1ee9 mu1ed7i nu0103m, ngu01b0u1eddi chu01a1i gu1ea7n nhu01b0 phu1ea3i lu00e0m viu1ec7c suu1ed1t 12 thu00e1ng. Anh Lu00ea Thu00f4ng Tu00ednh, u0111u1ed9i tru01b0u1edfng u0111u1ed9i cu00e2y kiu1ec3ng cho hay, cu1ee9 mu1ed7i ngu00e0y tu01b0u1edbi 2 lu01b0u1ee3t, 10 ngu00e0y phun thuu1ed1c tru1eeb su00e2u, nu1ea5m 1 lu1ea7n, 1 thu00e1ng lu1ea1i 1 lu1ea7n bu00f3n phu00e2n cho mai... Khu00f3 nhu1ea5t trong cu00e1c khu00e2u vu1eabn lu00e0 cu00f4ng u0111ou1ea1n u0111u1ec3 mai ra hoa u0111u00fang vu00e0o du1ecbp Tu1ebft. u00c9p mai tru1ed3ng trong chu1eadu ra hoa theo u00fd muu1ed1n thu00ec khu1ea3 nu0103ng thu00e0nh cu00f4ng u0111u1ebfn 90% nhu01b0ng vu1edbi mai tru1ed3ng ngou00e0i vu01b0u1eddn thu00ec khu00f4ng du00e1m chu1eafc. Du00f9 u0111u00e3 thu1ef1c hiu1ec7n u0111u00fang theo ku1ef9 thuu1eadt nhu01b0ng chuyu1ec7n mai nu1edf tru1eadt ngu00e0y lu00e0 chuyu1ec7n bu00ecnh thu01b0u1eddng, bu1edfi u0111u00f4i khi cu00f2n phu1ea3i phu1ee5 thuu1ed9c vu00e0o thu1eddi tiu1ebft.</div>n","short_description":"<p><strong>Huu1ebf khu00f4ng phu1ea3i lu00e0 u0111u1ecba phu01b0u01a1ng duy nhu1ea5t tru1ed3ng mai, chu01a1i mai. Nhu01b0ng khu00f4ng phu1ea3i vu00f4 cu1edb mu00e0 giu1eefa mu1ed9t &#8220;tu1eadp u0111ou00e0n&#8221; mai Bu00ecnh u0110u1ecbnh, Phu00fa Yu00ean, cu00e1c tu1ec9nh miu1ec1n Tu00e2y Nam bu1ed9 hay thu1eadm chu00ed cu1ea3 mai ru1eebng Bu00ecnh Thuu1eadn tu1ecfa su1eafc khoe hu01b0u01a1ng thu00ec mai vu00e0ng xu1ee9 Huu1ebf &#8211; Hou00e0ng Mai, Mai Ngu1ef1 &#8211; vu1eabn u0111u01b0u1ee3c du00e2n su00e0nh u0111iu1ec7u nhu1eafc u0111u1ebfn nhiu1ec1u nhu1ea5t.</strong></p>n","reviews_allowed":true,"average_rating":"0.00","rating_count":0,"related_ids":[],"upsell_ids":[],"cross_sell_ids":[],"parent_id":0,"categories":["Bu00e1n mai Tu1ebft","Mai vu00e0ng"],"tags":["mai-hue"],"images":[{"id":62,"created_at":"2015-03-23T08:46:50Z","updated_at":"2015-03-23T08:46:50Z","src":"http://localhost/saigonhoa/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/maihue.jpg","title":"maihue","alt":"","position":0}],"featured_src":"http://localhost/saigonhoa/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/maihue.jpg","attributes":[],"downloads":[],"download_limit":0,"download_expiry":0,"download_type":"","purchase_note":"<p>Chu1ea5t lu01b0u1ee3ng : quu00ed hiu1ebfm</p>n","total_sales":3,"variations":[],"parent":[]}}'),
